title: Did you catch Florida Labs for not reporting Coved 19's negative results?
subtitle: The percentage rates of positive results have become confused in some laboratories, but one thing remains clear: COVID-19 cases were rising in Florida in July 2020.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: Thirty-three Florida Labs were arrested for "cooking books" or tampering with data after not reporting negative COVID-19 test results between March and July 2020.
